<item>
 <title>Capacity Building and Interactive Communication</title>
 <link>http://transmissionproject.org/resources/2010/9/capacity-building-and-interactive-communication</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Developing on a previous article about Digital Arts Service Corps alumni’s experiences with Salesforce implementation projects, this case study of Appalshop explores the decision-making process behind a database implementation in order to make explicit the connection between the construction of an online database and the advancement of an organization’s&amp;nbsp;mission.  &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
